blank">个人作品</a>。*(9)</li>	<li><a href="http://www.qianmu.org/资金证明" target="_blank">资金证明</a>：待收到录取通知之后递交。*(5)</li></ul><p>联系方式：</p><p>140 Commonwealth Avenue, Devlin Hall 208</p><p>Chestnut Hill, MA&nbsp; 02467-3809</p><p>Phone: (617) 552-3100</p><p>Toll Free: (800) 360-2522</p><p>Fax: (617) 552-0798</p><p>Contact: John Mahoney, Director of Undergraduate Admission*(2)</p><p><strong>费用与奖学金</strong></p><p>波士顿学院一年的花费将近7.5万美金，学校不向国际学生提供<a href="http://www.qianmu.org/Need-based" target="_blank">Need-based</a>奖学金。该校设立有限的Merit-based奖学金，也就是加贝利校长奖学金（The Gabelli Presidential Scholarship），覆盖全部学费，仅向通过EA方式申请的学生授予，每年只有20个名额。该奖学金自动随Offer发放，无需单独申请。国际学生须在获得录取通知后，递交资金证明。*(4)(5)(10)</p><table border="1" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">	<tbody>		<tr>			<td style="width:23.04%">			<p>支出项目</p>			</td>			<td style="width:55.76%">			<p>项目英文名</p>			</td>			<td style="width:21.18%">			<p>2019-20学年费用</p>			</td>		</tr>		<tr>			<td style="width:23.04%">			<p>学费</p>			</td>			<td style="width:55.76%">			<p>Tuition and fees</p>			</td>			<td style="width:21.18%">			<p>$56,780+$1,705</p>			</td>		</tr>		<tr>			<td style="width:23.04%">			<p>住宿费用</p>			</td>			<td style="width:55.76%">			<p>Room and board</p>			</td>			<td style="width:21.18%">			<p>$14,826</p>			</td>		</tr>		<tr>			<td style="width:23.04%">			<p>书本费</p>			</td>			<td style="width:55.76%">			<p>Books and supplies</p>			</td>			<td style="width:21.18%">			<p>$2,850</p>			</td>		</tr>		<tr>			<td style="width:23.04%">个人花费</td>			<td style="width:55.76%">Personal expenses</td>			<td style="width:21.18%">			<p>$5,200</p>			</td>		</tr>		<tr>			<td style="width:23.04%">			<p>合计</p>			</td>			<td style="width:55.76%">			<p>Estimated Total</p>			</td>			<td style="width:21.18%">			<p>$78,511</p>			</td>		</tr>	</tbody></table><p>*(3)</p><h2>转学申请</h2><p><strong>基本信息：</strong></p><table border="1" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">	<tbody>		<tr>			<td style="width:18.96%">			<p>TOEFL要求</p>			</td>			<td style="width:15.16%">			<p>100</p>			<