i>算术组上同调（the cohomology of arithmetic groups）</li>	<li>品种几何（the geometry of Shimura varieties）</li>	<li>局部朗兰兹对应关系（the local Langlands correspondence）</li>	<li>多重狄数系列（multiple Dirichlet series）</li>	<li>表示理论（representation theory）</li>	<li>代数几何（algebraic geometry）</li>	<li>光谱几何（spectral geometry）*(6)</li></ul><p>外部链接：</p><ul>	<li>数学系研究生申请手册：<a href="http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=FrFYCW9ELAtGuVcKsssssIIKeEBvW9Mb-VeUeUuWEvdMlq_cvHIpYs5glk57l-p_5TdLc6a5C6WyUThibc_i-wf62WN6gYINy_-5ReSH9S6vD9e4qu6-3Abcm" target="_blank">Mathematics Application Brochure</a>(PDF)</li></ul><p>参考资料：</p><p>(1) <a href="http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=4rjT-BD2wjNSrTTJhKkkKDfwE07AZOEhpHWxybPG1YQd-ki7yd7c7UhH_ahP22bDk6vB8i65yLF0F9E0kUhUfdykxGKnGazZRoCh_qN1yl5qkpR3" target="_blank">Department Requirements</a>&nbsp;Boston College</p><p>(2) <a href="http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=lreSUw0aLhsIeJWMIIIIII950qNKtiOY1s1sx-JCx-6S0jOKRw-gmyTjDuTsDy5SVy50m9XSgMfSNOViN6KQx3CBbeC_vOfQWOoQ-IE7a" target="_blank">International Applicants</a>&nbsp;Boston College</p><p>(3) <a href="http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=IrnDV7pgwEi9Xud-FFFFF5dfGYO4BieEnTnT8J942-AXysSnMrxc8rD8_Po8t1xCHKU05pz8sPa09-U05hl8fpFbfPa8sPa0wRL09WMtL-yavLNaFX8VvHDl6qDQ6zJ89s" target="_blank">Application Requirements</a>&nbsp;Boston College</p><p>(4) <a href="http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=_r75g1XZw9P-FArJBWm0URfQKV3YZTt145iKVuARfa4sEMxr5fIlWajiezzzPvBOoGAdYHgBrOGEBhTcT4g46zzE7GnvPsONqFr7cTmFx6b3OGgBhD9N0nTDMfIoKcZFKQ14fk9FVpGOU1" target="_blank">Financial Aid</a>&nbsp;Boston College</p><p>(5) <a href="http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=BraKR4YOwp7HowU2VVVVVVk4aMacsXHhmgJgJvPGfvPRFM1hsUbHpUNjsvNAf95hpY-cT3Noh8CX_khXxDjqbkI5e" target="_blank">Graduate Program</a>&nbsp;Boston College</p><p>(6) <a href="http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=SrWl9Lujk78ysUq8v3z0mKY1TH_x4V6YGvxZb-PfCtIYLWtYgYlgVOtJ2f_gtAGAAOvRpW0pzTaB3An3EuZmACrOJ0WcnVmaXN1WS3U_ghmAlf3gCtO4sQc_" target="_blank">PhD Program</a>&nbsp;Boston College</p><p>&nbsp;</p><