qianmu.org/数学" target="_blank">数学</a>和生物）。该学位与艺术与科学研究生院联合开设，学科包括：</p><ul>	<li>生物学（Biology）</li>	<li><a href="http://www.qianmu.org/化学" target="_blank">化学</a>（<a href="http://www.qianmu.org/化学" target="_blank">Chemistry</a>）</li>	<li><a href="http://www.qianmu.org/地质学" target="_blank">地质学</a>或<a href="http://www.qianmu.org/地球科学" target="_blank">地球科学</a>（Geology/<a href="http://www.qianmu.org/地球科学" target="_blank">Earth Science</a>）</li>	<li><a href="http://www.qianmu.org/物理" target="_blank">物理</a>学（<a href="http://www.qianmu.org/物理" target="_blank">Physics</a>）</li>	<li>英语（English）</li>	<li>拉丁与古典<a href="http://www.qianmu.org/人类学" target="_blank">人类学</a>（Latin and Classical Humanities）</li>	<li>历史（<a href="http://www.qianmu.org/历史" target="_blank">History</a>）</li>	<li>数学（<a href="http://www.qianmu.org/数学" target="_blank">Mathematics</a>）</li></ul><p><strong>专业设置</strong></p><table border="1" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">	<tbody>		<tr>			<td style="width:125px">			<p>课程设计与教学</p>			</td>			<td style="width:494px">			<p>Curriculum and Instruction (M.Ed. Phd)</p>			</td>		</tr>		<tr>			<td style="width:125px">			<p>早教</p>			</td>			<td style="width:494px">			<p>Early Childhood Teaching (M.Ed.)</p>			</td>		</tr>		<tr>			<td style="width:125px">			<p>初等师范教育</p>			</td>			<td style="width:494px">			<p>Elementary Teaching (M.Ed.)*</p>			</td>		</tr>		<tr>			<td style="width:125px">			<p>阅读与写作</p>			</td>			<td style="width:494px">			<p>Reading/Literacy (M.Ed.)</p>			</td>		</tr>		<tr>			<td style="width:125px">			<p>中等师范教育</p>			</td>			<td style="width:494px">			<p>Secondary Education (M.Ed., M.A.T., M.S.T.)*</p>			</td>		</tr>		<tr>			<td style="width:125px">			<p>特殊教育</p>			</td>			<td style="width:494px">			<p>Special Education (M.Ed.)**</p>			</td>		</tr>		<tr>			<td style="width:125px">			<p>宗教教育</p>			</td>			<td style="width:494px">			<p>Religious Education (M.Ed.)(offered through the School of Theology and Ministry)</p>			</td>		</tr>	</tbody></table><p>*(1)</p